Package com.javadude.annotation

Enum Summary
Access Describes the access level of generated getter and setter methods.
PropertyKind Describes the kinds of properties that you can define using JavaDude Annotations.
 

Annotation Types Summary
Bean An annotation that requests to generate Bean code for the annotated class.
Delegate Defines a type (interface or class) for which you want to generate delegation methods.
Expose Marks a method to expose via an extracted interface.
ExtractInterface Flags a class to have an interface created for.
NullObject Specifies a java interface that will be implemented using Null Object methods.
Observer Defines an event set to generate code for.
Property Defines a property for a JavaBean.
